# Stock Portfolio Tracker  

A Python-based **Stock Portfolio Tracker** that allows users to monitor stock performance, track investments, and analyze portfolio trends in real time.  

## Features  
- Add and manage stocks in a portfolio  
- Fetch real-time stock prices using an API  
- Calculate profit/loss and track performance  
- View historical trends and data visualization  
- User-friendly interface  

## Technologies Used  
- **Python**  
- **Requests (for fetching stock data)**  
- **Pandas (for data processing)**  
- **Matplotlib / Plotly (for visualizations)**  
